HEADWORD: Amole
<hw>A*mo"le</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Mex.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Any detergent plant, or the part of it used as a
detergent, as the roots of <spn>Agave Americana</spn>, <spn>Chlorogalum
pomeridianum</spn>, etc.</def> <mark>[Sp. Amer. & Mex.]</mark>⟦br⟧
